		,"99.99% 7Li, onto thin formvar substrates. Typical"
		,"target thickness was - 100 microg/cm2. To reduce"
		,"oxidation the targets were kept under vacuum at all"
		,"times by means of an enclosing target holder which"
		,"fitted vacuum locks on both the evaporation bell jar"
		,"and the scattering chamber."]
